	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Mon, Sep 24th 12:08 AM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.45]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>I have a level 15 monk and need suggestions for armor and equipment upgrades.&nbsp;&nbsp;Here is what i have so far...<br><br>Ears: Orc fang earrings<br>Neck: Orc fang neclace<br>Head: Executioner's Hood<br>Face: Wu's Mask<br>Rings: Velium Fire Wedding Rings<br>Wrist 1: Hardened Kodiak Leather Bracer<br>Wrist 2: Wu bracer<br>Arm: Wu's arms<br>Shoulder: Drolvarg Mantle<br>Chest: CCS<br>Back: Spider Fur cloak<br>Waist: SPider Fur Belt<br>Gloves: Gem inlaid gauntlets<br>Leggings: Wu leggings<br>Boots: Ulthork Boots<br>Primary: Wu stick<br>Offhand: Knuckle Duster<br>Range: nothing<br><br>I was also wondering if i should do the kromrif military leggings quest. Do the stats on kromrif leggings make up for the weight?<br>Please give me some reasonable equipment upgrades i should get...Thanks)<br><br>Lothaine, vicar<br>Shassix, n00b monk<br><br>Druzzil Ro~<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
	   <span style='font-weight: normal; font-size: 9px;'>[<a href=#top>Top</a>]</span></tr>
